          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "To beat out all the other sports cars, the Mustang achieved a score of 76 out of 100. In most grading systems that’s a C, but apparently for Consumer Reports it’s an A+. Go figure.",
